    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, glass-like luster with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks, while the wheels are entirely free of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in perfect state; the leather is supple without any creasing, all electronics function perfectly, and it still carries that new-car scent. Every maintenance record is accounted for, confirming that this car has been meticulously garaged and cared for by a single owner. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-grade example that requires absolutely nothing.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
